These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, collecting, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, ice-hockey
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, marigold, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, june, october
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, brazilian, spanish
 1. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's hobby is chess and the spanish##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the spanish##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the mexican is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who growsmarigold##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the brazilian##1
 7. the argentine is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Hobby           | collecting | chess   | writing | photography |
| Sport   | climbing      | cricket | cycling              | ice-hockey |
| Flower   | tulip       | poppy     | dahlia               | marigold    |
| Birthday           | september        | june     | october           | august       |
| Nationality     | argentine | brazilian     | mexican                | spanish      |

