The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, december, march
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, rock-climbing, camping
 1. the person driving the van is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the train is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
