There are 4 different nationalities: italian, dutch, german, british
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, january, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is the italian##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the italian and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 6. the british is on the far left##1
 7. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the horse##2
10. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes white is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| City      | miami     | marseilles | liverpool    | venice          |
