There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, purple, lavender, lilac
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growspurpleing##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is between the egyptian and the person who likes lavender##2
 3. the japanese is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the japanese is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who likes lilac is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the japanese is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the turkish is on the left of the person who growspurpleing##1
11. the person who growspurpleing is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who likes lilac##2
12. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | august      | january         | february | june      |
| City           | hamburg | rome | paris | london     |
| Nationality   | turkish         | japanese          | french  | egyptian |
| Flower         | balloon-flower        | purpleing  | amaryllis | bellflower   |
| Color     | purple    | lavender         | lilac     | light-blue     |

