.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, april, may
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, blend, alhambra
City: paris, prague, new-york, nizza
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, spanish, french, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, ambient, gospel
 1. the person traveling to nizza is between the french and the fan electronic##2
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the spanish is the fan ambient##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
 5. the nigerian is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the fan d&b##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is between the alhambra-smoker and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
