.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, poker, canasta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, davidoff, old-henry
City: edinburgh, rome, prague, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: banana, eggplant, cucumber, corn
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, yellow, mauve, emerald
 1. the person traveling to prague is the aristoff-smoker##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person playing snooker is between the person eating corn and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing snooker and the person who likes emerald##2
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person playing poker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
