.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, sunflower, poppy
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, kale, pumpkin, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, writer, entrepreneur, doctor
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, bongani, ritmeester
House: wooden, gothic-revival, victorian, art-deco
 1. the person eating raspberry is the writer##1
 2. the art-deco house is between the doctor and the dunhill-smoker##2
 3. the gothic-revival house is between the alhambra-smoker and the victorian house##2
 4. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the person eating pumpkin is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the victorian house##1
10. the person who growsazalea is the videographer##1
11. the videographer is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Flower         | sunflower  | orchid | poppy | azalea |
| Food   | raspberry      | kale   | pumpkin      | pineapple    |
| Job   | writer  | entrepreneur | doctor        | videographer     |
| Cigar         | dunhill  | alhambra  | bongani     | ritmeester      |
| House     | wooden | art-deco      | gothic-revival   | victorian       |

 